<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-CN">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <link
      rel="stylesheet"
      href="https://cdn.staticfile.net/twitter-bootstrap/5.1.1/css/bootstrap.min.css"
    />
    <title>CRA-STUDiO</title>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div>
      <div style="background-color: rgb(33, 37, 41)">
        <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-md bg-dark navbar-dark container">
          <a class="navbar-brand" href="/">CRA-STUDiO</a>

          <button
            class="navbar-toggler"
            type="button"
            data-bs-toggle="collapse"
            data-bs-target="#collapsibleNavbar"
          >
            <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
          </button>

          <div
            class="collapse navbar-collapse justify-content-end"
            id="collapsibleNavbar"
            style="background-color: rgb(33, 37, 41)"
          >
            <ul class="navbar-nav">
              <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link" href="/">首页</a>
              </li>
              <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link" href="#">接入文档</a>
              </li>
              <li class="nav-item">
                <a class="nav-link" href="#">关于</a>
              </li>
              {{if .Logined}}
              <li class="nav-item">
                <button onclick="window.location.href='/panel'" class="btn btn-primary">控制台</button>
              </li>
              <li class="nav-item">
                <p style="color:#f5f5f5;">欢迎回来，{{.Username}}</p>
              </li>
              {{else}}
              <li class="nav-item">
                <button onclick="window.location.href='/login'" class="btn btn-primary">登陆</button>
              </li>
              <li class="nav-item">
                <button onclick="window.location.href='/register'" class="btn btn-primary">注册</button>
              </li>
              {{end}}
            </ul>
          </div>
        </nav>
      </div>
      <div
        style="
          height: 500px;
          background-image: url(static/img/bg_icon.jpg);
          background-size: 100% 100%;
        "
      >
        <div class="container" style="text-align: center; color: #f5f5f5">
          <h1 style="padding-top: 120px">一切献给，委员会</h1>
          <p>
            「我来编程、我来调试、我来打造卓越的游戏体验」「我任凭技术挑战拨转轮盘，全力以赴。历经艰难困境而后成就辉煌」一切献给，委员会
          </p>
          <div style="padding-top: 10px">
            <button onclick="window.location.href='/panel'" class="btn btn-primary" style="width: 130px">控制台</button>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://cdn.staticfile.net/popper.js/2.9.3/umd/popper.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.staticfile.net/twitter-bootstrap/5.1.1/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
  </body>
</html>
